{"tid":2386303,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"CCL最新報175.04點，按周跌0.63%，創10個月新低","createTime":"2021-01-29T13:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T11:00:49.000Z","uid":83582,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ff6773589cce1a3cefa58f386a9c06892c6ea04a","tid":2386303,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:19:01.000Z","msg":"CCL連跌三周 中原料樓價即將反覆上升<br />\n2020年1月29日<br />\n<br />\n疫情下樓價偏軟，反映整體二手樓價的中原城市領先指數CCL，最新報175.04點，按周跌0.63%，創10個月新低。指數已連跌三周，累跌1.7%。<br />\n<br />\n中原地產研究部高級聯席董事黃良昇指出，早前四區CCL_Mass連續兩周三區跌、一區升，但今周兩區升兩區跌，相信整體樓價即將反覆上升。最近5周新界兩區樓價走勢持續一升一跌，準備突破向上。展望樓價升勢會由新界兩區逐步蔓延至港九市區，帶領未來整體樓價反覆向升。<br />\n<br />\n新界東CCL_Mass最新報186.97點，按周升0.16%，近5周持續一升一跌。新界西CCL_Mass報162.28點，按周跌2.72%，近6周持續一升一跌。港島CCL_Mass報183.87點，按周升0.63%，終止兩周連跌。九龍CCL_Mass報171.45點，按周跌0.37%，連跌3周共2.98%。<br />\n<br />\n(節錄, 完整文章請看蘋果)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210129/GQUZPC62TREX7IO2BK4V57QHLY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210129%2FGQUZPC62TREX7IO2BK4V57QHLY%2F&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VHxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=69db94b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210129%2FGQUZPC62TREX7IO2BK4V57QHLY%2F&h=0139d991\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210129/GQUZPC62TREX7IO2BK4V57QHLY/</a>"},{"pid":"04eecc2237665a5c1952c92d1c9f5564d8e48ec9","tid":2386303,"uid":165891,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:45:07.000Z","msg":"其實有冇料過一次樓價唔係升 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78568bb70f852c2db617b79ae80065374ce90171","tid":2386303,"uid":85502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04eecc2237665a5c1952c92d1c9f5564d8e48ec9","tid":2386303,"uid":165891,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:45:07.000Z","msg":"其實有冇料過一次樓價唔係升 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"re